        "content_position": "middleLeft",
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<h3>“We just loved having all of our people in one place… <em>I think on the day we both realised how blessed we are.</em> To have a circle of people around us that are all connected, and <em>love each other as much as they love us.</em>”</h3>",
